snippet.title: Death Rings of Jupiter - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Available on Steam for $1.99USD
http://store.steampowered.com/app/691620/Death_Rings_of_Jupiter/

Death Rings of Jupiter is a 2d retro bullet hell shooter, set in the dense asteroid fields that make up the rings of Jupiter.
It features original gameplay that mixes classic gravity games and platformers.

Music "Seven" by Vi-res http://discocinematic.bandcamp.com

By Albatross Wirehead 2017 wirehead.com.au
